IfW Sees German Tax Cuts as ‘Insufficient,’ Handelsblatt Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-12-13T17:41:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-13/ifw-sees-german-tax-cuts-as-insufficient-handelsblatt-says.html
Germany ’s IfW Institute sees the
planned tax cuts by the country’s government as “totally
insufficient,”  Handelsblatt  reported today in a preview of an
article that will be published tomorrow, citing an IfW study.  To contact the reporter on this story:
